javax.telephony.privatedata

Interface PrivateDataAddressListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AddressListener, java.util.EventListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PrivateDataAddressListenerAdapter

    public interface PrivateDataAddressListener
extends AddressListener
    The PrivateDataAddressListener interface reports the receipt of platform-specific address information. This interface extends the AddressListener interfaces.
    Since:
    1.4
    See Also:
    AddressListener, PrivateData, PrivateDataEvent
